<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Db_Table_Row_Abstract and Zend_Db_Table_Rowset_Abstract both provide setTable() methods, but there appears to be no way to get to the table object once it has been set.</p>

<p>Is this by design, and if so, for what reasons do we not expose this currently write-only property?</p>

